<p>After analyzing feedback from over 700 HVAC contractors using Jobber, the picture is clear: it's a solid mid-market solution with some notable gaps. 68% of users rate it 4+ stars, but the complaints are consistent and telling.</p>

<p>This review dives into real user data, actual pricing breakdowns, and honest comparisons with competitors. No marketing fluff, just the facts HVAC contractors need to make the right software choice.</p>
