<h2 id="overview">Jobber Overview & Pricing</h2>

<div class="prose max-w-none">
<p>Jobber serves over 100,000 service businesses, including roughly 8,000 HVAC contractors. Founded in 2011, it's positioned as an all-in-one solution for scheduling, invoicing, payments, and customer management.</p>

<p>The platform handles the basics well but lacks HVAC-specific features like equipment lifecycle tracking, detailed maintenance agreements, and advanced inventory management. Most HVAC users are small to medium-sized companies (3-25 technicians) who value simplicity over specialized functionality.</p>

